item.description:
So you couldn't make it to the Burning Man Festival this year. In the same spirit of free expression, come sing out at our own "Singing Person Festival".

This is the first SingFree Session, but as I mentioned, it is still Karaoke-Do. Some people prefer a more "serious" name, it seems.

Space is limited, which means a small, supportive crowd.

Session is 7-9pm.

Looking forward to seeing and hearing you!
item.how_to_find_us: Ask at the front desk for the SingFree Session (or the "karaoke class"), and please sign in there.
